

### **📌 JIO Coin DEX - Decentralized Exchange on Polygon Amoy**  

![JIO Coin DEX](https://your-image-url.com) _(Optional: Add a project logo or screenshot)_

## **🔹 Overview**  
JIO Coin DEX is a **decentralized exchange (DEX)** built on **Polygon Amoy Testnet** that allows users to trade JIO Coins securely. It includes:  
- **Smart Contract** written in **Rust (Ink!)**, deployed on **Polygon Amoy**.  
- **Backend** in **Node.js** for managing API interactions.  
- **Frontend** built with **React.js** for a seamless UI.  


## **🔹 Tech Stack**  
| Layer        | Technology |
|-------------|------------|
| **Blockchain**  | Polygon Amoy Testnet |
| **Smart Contract** | Rust (Ink!) |
| **Backend** | Node.js, Express.js |
| **Frontend** | React.js, Web3.js, Ethers.js |
| **Package Manager** | NPM |
| **Version Control** | Git & GitHub |


## **🔹 Project Structure**  

jio_dex_project/
│── jio_dex_backend/      # Backend Node.js server
│── jio_dex_frontend/     # Frontend React.js UI
│── JioDex/               # Smart contract (Rust, Ink!)

## **🔹 Installation & Setup**  

### **1️⃣ Clone the Repository**  

git clone https://github.com/YourGitHubUsername/jio_dex_project.git
cd jio_dex_project

### **2️⃣ Smart Contract Setup (Ink!)**

cd JioDex/jio_coin
cargo +nightly contract build

✅ **Output:** `jio_coin.contract` file generated.  

📌 **Deploy using Remix IDE** with contract: `0x3081075617E13A3fd0B03d20A7a1bB6793E14BE4`  


**3️⃣ Backend Setup (Node.js & Express)**
cd ../jio_dex_backend
npm install
node index.js
✅ **Output:** `JIO DEX Backend running on port 5000`  


### **4️⃣ Frontend Setup (React.js)**

cd ../jio_dex_frontend
npm install
npm start

✅ **Output:** React UI should open at `http://localhost:3000/`  


## **🔹 Usage Guide**  

### **💰 Trading JIO Coins**  
1️⃣ Connect MetaMask to **Polygon Amoy Testnet**  
2️⃣ Load **JIO Coin DEX Frontend**  
3️⃣ Select **Buy/Sell JIO Coins**  
4️⃣ Confirm the transaction in MetaMask  


